so yea ive recently decided, due to concerns of friends whos opinions matter that im stuck in a rut, that i must change my life, thuse far ive decided once im done with the current carton of cigs i still have in my possession i will be quitting, this is not to appease others its mostly cause its a f'ing expensive habit and im sick of waking up and coughing for an hour before being able to breathe properly plus i miss singing and smoking fucks my voice hardcore, ive also decided that i dislike my job and will be doing something to rectify my employment woes, also cleaning my room as it has not been cleaned once in the 10 months ive lived there, now that just means ive got clothes and movies and various crap everywhere trash is removed on a semi daily basis so its not trash just crap, also cleaning my car, same condition as room and its always bugged the hell out of me but have always just not cared if i wasnt dating someone, not to say that im dating anyone now which im not, dont feel like dating fora long while until i figure out how to be happy being alone and not just apathetic. so yea thats pretty much it, oh yea was in an accident at work the other night, was heading back to the werehouse and some dick ina tractor trailer started merging into my lane and dragged his trailer along the entire length of my work truck and knocked my mirror loose, and instead of stopping he sped up and tried to get away, so i did what any responsible adult would do, i floored it and chased his ass for 15 miles all the while on the phone with his "hows my driving" operator. when he finally did stop he kept saying it was my fault like i just willed his trailer to hit me, and then changed his story like 7 diferent times. so yea after over a year of working there i know have an accident on my record, its kinda neat i was like the only one who didnt have one, im now part of the fuck up club lol. oh and on a high note i was not injured and neither was he. tata

so yea against the will of every inch of my being i purchased trapt for the ps2 the other day, now for yall that dont know trapt is the 4th installment of the deception( hence the title im witty no?) series started by tecmo on the playstation, now this is a horribly addicting game whose main function is to kill people who are trying to kill me in horrible ways by laying traps, hence trapt tecmo's witty no?, now granted this would seem to get boring after a while but ive been playing it for a week and dear me i just cant stop, nothing is more entertaing to me right now then setting up a spring board and launching a foe ,hehe i said foe, into an electric chair who then rebounds into the guilotine ive laid and thrown by the force into a wall of molten metal and finally shot with an arrow, yea overkill and anti-climactic to boot but eh what can ya do. i really dont know what the point of my posting lately is so i figure ill just post random events in my week from now on. this will get horribly interesting as no one will know if its made up or not. welcome to my head check your coat and hat at the door.

i am alone because i have chosen to set myself aside from humanity in order to better understand the things we do and why we do them. i alone am the cause of my lonelyness i alone am the reason why i feel like i cant relate to any one single person because i relate to everyone at the same time. it is impossible to hate or love or even fear people when i am trying to figure out who they are and what their function in the machine of life is.

i sit staring at the hole in my imaginatoin that has been there for as long as i can remember, i have no creative outlets anymore and whenerv i feel the need to create o or or wriute or do pretty much anything that would utilize my imagination outside of just talking im stifled and canty write or draw,m not that i draw all that well anyways so i thenwithdraw into myself and find myself hating what ive become and who i am and i cant for the life of me understand why7 or when i lost the abillity to communicate what i feel or express through words and sights what i want the world to understand, im a normal hunman being so what if my brain oprates on a tottally different wavelenght of creativity then the rest of society anmd blah blah blah to all of those who expect me to do something great and wonderous with my life, well i cant i dont know what i want or who i am and ill never be able to figure it out until the day my brain stops doing the things that it does, but who knows maybe i am the person im supposed to be and everyone else needs to catch up. am i a jump in mental awareness. or am i just fucked. i miss being able to feel like im aprt of those arouind me and no matter how hard i try and cant get close to them, most of them would say its because i fear rejecetion, which yes i do but that shouldnt be the only reason, there has to be some reason i refuse to let anyone get to close to me as in llike emotionally speaking, i dont know what happend but all i know is i am still awake and thses are the thoughts running through my head, why cant i be like everyone else whjy cant i let those i love know i love them why cant i let anyone get close, why do i feel like im supposed to be doing something great with my life but refuse to go out and do anything about it, why why fucking why. damn im whiny. but still. i want to be feel like a worthwhile individual i want to know i wont be forgotten as easily as i tend to forget people, there ate literaly legions of people ive forgotten over the years and i dont know why i forgot them, did they piss me off, were they just not important enough to me why am i the person i see in the mirror what made me become this shadow of humanity, why am i delighted and afraid of my abilty to just melt into the background and not be noticed. my name is andrew and i dont know who i am or how i came to be here. i miss the loved ones in my life but cant bring to be around them because i feel like ive failed them and i dont know how or why i feel this way. i miss so many people but everyday i want nothing more then to just fade away but at the same time im afraid to. i dont want to feel anymore but i cant bring myself to shut off my emotions again i didnt like feeling dead inside but everyday its the same thing and i feel like i allready have. im such a whiny whiny person and i think this is one of the longest entries ive ever made. im tired of feeling apathetic but i cant find a way to be anything else. im in a constant state of just existing, ive no desire to actualy try and change anything in my life and everytime i do i fight so fucking hard against the change. i want to have a goal i want to have something to live for all i have right now is to keep me going is the desire to wake up and there are days when i dont even want to do that. the high point of my day as many can attest to is the fact that i woke up. nothing more nothing less. i want more out of life but dont know how to get it.
